metadata.name: Amor Fati: Peace
metadata.description:
Amor Fati: Peace by Jordan Cuellar
Hand drawn digital piece
Blue colorway
4000 x 4000 px

Amor Fati is a latin expression for "love of fate" or "love of one's fate." A mindset to embrace what you go through (whether good or bad) and make the best of your situation.

What does this phrase mean to you?

Collector will receive:
• Hi-res image
• Hi-res pdf
• 12x12 inch framed print (by request)
